{"prompt": "Develop an engaging platform for a community arts and crafts center. The primary color should be a lively fuchsia.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Community Arts & Crafts Hub</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e1007e; /* Lively Fuchsia */\n            --secondary-color: #f8c8d4; /* A softer pink */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #ff99cc;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--accent-color) 100%);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .card h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: block;\n            width: fit-content;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        #gallery img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        #gallery .gallery-item {\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Community Arts & Crafts Hub</h1>\n        <p>Igniting creativity, together!</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#classes\">Workshops</a>\n        <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"about\">\n        <h2>Welcome to Our Hub!</h2>\n        <p>We are a vibrant space dedicated to fostering creativity and connection through the arts and crafts. Whether you're a seasoned artist or a curious beginner, our community is here to inspire and support your artistic journey.</p>\n        <p>Join us for a variety of workshops, open studio sessions, and community events designed to spark imagination and build lasting friendships.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"classes\">\n        <h2>Upcoming Workshops</h2>\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <h3>Introduction to Pottery</h3>\n            <p><strong>Date:</strong> October 28, 2023</p>\n            <p><strong>Time:</strong> 10:00 AM - 1:00 PM</p>\n            <p>Learn the basics of hand-building and wheel throwing.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <h3>Watercolor Painting for Beginners</h3>\n            <p><strong>Date:</strong> November 4, 2023</p>\n            <p><strong>Time:</strong> 2:00 PM - 4:30 PM</p>\n            <p>Explore vibrant colors and techniques to create your own masterpiece.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <h3>Knitting & Crochet Circle</h3>\n            <p><strong>Date:</strong> Every Saturday</p>\n            <p><strong>Time:</strong> 11:00 AM - 1:00 PM</p>\n            <p>A casual gathering for yarn enthusiasts of all levels.</p>\n        </div>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View Full Schedule & Register</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"gallery\">\n        <h2>Community Showcase</h2>\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e1007e/ffffff?text=Pottery+Art\" alt=\"Pottery Artwork\">\n                <h4>Handcrafted Pottery</h4>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f8c8d4/333333?text=Watercolor+Painting\" alt=\"Watercolor Painting\">\n                <h4>Vibrant Watercolors</h4>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/ff99cc/333333?text=Knitted+Scarf\" alt=\"Knitted Scarf\">\n                <h4>Cozy Knits</h4>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"contact\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Have questions or want to get involved? We'd love to hear from you!</p>\n        <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@artshub.com</p>\n        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Creative Lane, Artville, CA 90210</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Community Arts & Crafts Hub. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}